VARIABLES 
—---------------------
* Variables are the memory blocks or container.
* variables are used to store the data inside the memory blocks
* once we store the data we can reuse n -number of times


CHARACTERISTICS OF VARIABLES ➖
—------------------------------


  Int a=10


Int —--------> data type
a  —--------> variable name
Size —-----> 4bytes 
value—------> 10














Variables are involved in 3 steps ➖
—---------------------------------------
VARIABLE DECLARATION ➖
—-----------------------------------------------
SYNTAX -   data type var-name;
Ex:-  int   a;
