1.LOCAL VARIABLES ➖
—---------------------------------
 If user or programmer has  declared any variable inside the method ,block or constructor
Is known as “ local variables “
*  the scope of local variables is inside the particular block where we have declared
For local variables before utilization initialization is mandatory




Ex:-
—-
class Demo
{
public static void main(String []manoj)
{
int a;
a=10;
System.out.println(a);
String s;
s="james gosling";
System.out.println(s);
}
}


