RE-INTIALIZATION ➖
—-----------------------------
 If user or programmer wants to modify the value from existing value
Then we have to for “ reintialization “
Ex:-
—-
class Demo
{
public static void main(String []manoj)
{
String name="maya";
System.out.println(name);
name="sheela";
System.out.println(name);
}
}




FINAL ➖
—-----------
Final is a keyword
If user or programmer wants to fix the value through out the programme then we have to use “ final “ keyword while declaring the variable.
Ex:-
—--
class Demo
{
public static void main(String []manoj)
{
 final String name="kalyani priyadarshini";
System.out.println(name);
name=" sai pallavi";
System.out.println(name);


}
}
